response.overview: Morrissey @ Festival Viña del Mar, Chile 2012: I want the one I can't have - First of the gang to die - You're the one for me, Fatty - When last I spoke to Carol - Black Cloud - Speedway - There is a light that never goes out - Everyday is like sunday - I know It's over - Let me kiss you - People are the same everywhere - I'm throwing my arms around Paris - Meat is murder - Ouija board, Ouija board - I will see you in far-off places - Scandinavia - You have killed me - How soon is now
response.title: Morrissey: Festival Viña del Mar
